### CAF Core — REST Client (VS Code / IntelliJ)
### Set @base and @token in this file or your environment

@base = http://localhost:3847
@token = your-caf-core-token-if-auth-enabled

### Health (no auth)
GET {{base}}/health

### Rendering deps — RENDERER_BASE_URL / VIDEO_ASSEMBLY_BASE_URL this process uses + upstream /health (no auth)
GET {{base}}/health/rendering

### Decision plan (dry run — no trace write if dry_run true; trace written if false)
POST {{base}}/v1/decisions/plan
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

< ../examples/decisions-plan.request.json

### Ingest job
POST {{base}}/v1/jobs/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "project_slug": "SNS",
  "task_id": "SNS_2026W09__Instagram__FLOW_CAROUSEL__row0001__v1",
  "run_id": "SNS_2026W09",
  "flow_type": "FLOW_CAROUSEL",
  "platform": "Instagram",
  "pre_gen_score": 0.72
}

### Project constraints
PUT {{base}}/v1/projects/SNS/constraints
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "max_daily_jobs": 100,
  "min_score_to_generate": 0.35,
  "default_variation_cap": 2,
  "auto_validation_pass_threshold": 0.72
}

### Register prompt version
POST {{base}}/v1/prompt-versions
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "project_slug": "SNS",
  "flow_type": "FLOW_CAROUSEL",
  "prompt_id": "carousel_main",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "status": "active"
}

### --- Full run (signal pack → plan jobs → generate content) ---
### Prerequisites: migrations applied; OPENAI_API_KEY + DATABASE_URL on Core;
### RENDERER_BASE_URL (and VIDEO_ASSEMBLY for video) reachable from Core;
### SUPABASE_* for asset uploads; project has enabled flow types (project-config).

### List signal packs (use returned id for PATCH run)
GET {{base}}/v1/signal-packs/SNS
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

### Create run (status CREATED; attach pack via PATCH or include signal_pack_id here)
POST {{base}}/v1/runs/SNS
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "run_id": "SNS_2026W09",
  "source_window": "2026-W09"
}

### Attach signal pack (UUID from list or POST /v1/signal-packs/upload response)
PATCH {{base}}/v1/runs/SNS/SNS_2026W09
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "signal_pack_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Start run + process all jobs (LLM, QC, carousel/video render, assets)
POST {{base}}/v1/runs/SNS/SNS_2026W09/start-and-process
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{}

### Or: start only (creates PLANNED jobs), then process in a second call
# POST {{base}}/v1/runs/SNS/SNS_2026W09/start
# POST {{base}}/v1/runs/SNS/SNS_2026W09/process

### Process a single job by task_id
# POST {{base}}/v1/jobs/SNS/{{task_id}}/process

### Scene assembly — resume concat / TTS / mux only (uses rendered_scene_url on job; no new Sora clips)
POST {{base}}/v1/admin/scene-assembly-resume-pipeline
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "project_slug": "SNS",
  "task_id": "PASTE_TASK_ID_WITH_SCENE_URLS_ON_PAYLOAD"
}

### Scene assembly — merge from Supabase folder scenes/{run_id}/{task_id}/*.mp4 (no Sora; re-links scene order from files)
POST {{base}}/v1/admin/scene-assembly-merge-from-storage
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "project_slug": "SNS",
  "task_id": "PASTE_TASK_ID",
  "expand_voiceover": "never"
}

### Review queue (CAF Review app uses these; DB-backed, not Sheets)
GET {{base}}/v1/review-queue/SNS/counts
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

### All active projects (optional ?project_slug=SNS to narrow)
GET {{base}}/v1/review-queue-all/counts
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

GET {{base}}/v1/review-queue-all/in_review?limit=50&offset=0
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

### Tab: in_review | approved | rejected | needs_edit — optional ?limit=50&offset=0&run_id=SNS_2026W09
GET {{base}}/v1/review-queue/SNS/in_review?limit=50&offset=0
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

### Submit human decision (updates content_jobs.status + editorial_reviews)
POST {{base}}/v1/review-queue/SNS/task/PASTE_TASK_ID/decide
Content-Type: application/json
x-caf-core-token: {{token}}

{
  "decision": "APPROVED",
  "notes": "",
  "validator": "reviewer@example.com"
}
